commit a6c318ee505aeabe6f84e1543d68834b9e0e7acf
Author: Behdad Esfahbod <behdad@behdad.org>
Date:   Sun Dec 15 18:42:17 2013 -0500

    Bug 720379 - SIGFPE in pango_layout_iter_get_char_extents()

