Author: Matthias Clasen <mclasen@redhat.com>
Date:   Fri Sep 14 18:37:06 2012 -0400

    Load config file only once

 pango/pango-utils.c | 18 ++++++++++++------
 1 file changed, 12 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)

