commit dfd872568e3fb7dce3bc32410f8eb247899d5bc1
Author: Chun-wei Fan <fanchunwei@src.gnome.org>
Date:	Sun Sep 25 09:56:37 2011 +0800

    Update VS2008 PangoFT2 project

    This project will require the use of stdint.h, which is not shipped
    with
    VS2008 (but is shipped with VS2010), so define HAVE_STDINT_H for all
    settings in this project so that the stdint.h bundled in
    $(srcroot)/build/win32/vs9 will be used when HarfBuzz and FontConfig
    is
    being used.

 build/win32/vs9/pangoft2.vcprojin | 8 ++++----
