commit 775dd4e33c14560fc10cc0ad323163ac3450f959
Author: Chun-wei Fan <fanchunwei@src.gnome.org>
Date:	Fri Sep 16 16:00:51 2011 +0800

    hb-private.h: Fix compilation on newer GLib versions

    g_atomic_int_exchange_and_add was deprecated in the GLib gatomic.c
    rewrite,
    for GLib 2.29.6, so use g_atomic_int_add for GLib versions 2.29.5+.

 pango/opentype/hb-private.h | 4 ++++
