commit c43c4884bf4b405f58a0c966384ee751f82ee69c
Author: Chun-wei Fan <fanchunwei@src.gnome.org>
Date:	Mon May 16 17:52:41 2011 +0800

    Various Visual C++ support updates

    -Move the stub stdint.h back into the vs9 folder as stdint.h is
    shipped
     with Visual C++ 2010, and update the corresponding Makefile.am's
     accordingly
    -Add new solution to build Pango with FontConfig-the former solution
    file
     will build Pango without FontConfig.  This is to simplify the use
     of the GTK+ stack as many will probably not use FontConfig on
     Windows,
     therefore this is to reduce the number of dependencies
    -Added configurations in Pango, PangoWin32, PangoCairo regarding
    FontConfig
     (To make sure their configurations are consistent across the board)
    -Cleaned up the various project files for a bit.

